,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:47:52.000Z","msg":"近年真係鷲哥,overact得嚟好有壓場感,好過癮"},{"pid":"556d241a04de46c9fe53e6a5f8480ff5688114c0","tid":440111,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">劉邦!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"39eff30da4374c38d039131236cbbc665167a913","tid":440111,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近年真係鷲哥,overact得嚟好有壓場感,好過癮</blockquote><br />\n入黎就係想講鷲哥 見到真人都係營住佢都係好似高天鷲咁既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e412ea4fcc8c9bd63cc53f8eeac0e4fc1d96ca20","tid":440111,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"206f9e08bc78fd30593d39a9d05ec56974a7a589","tid":440111,"uid":13946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"江華，九五至尊<br />\n張衛健，西遊記<br />\n黃秋生，伊波拉病毒<br />\n肥溫，鐵達尼號"},{"pid":"09329bedf1fd62d93ff5789a82c1ee711edaf59a","tid":440111,"uid":143427,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"黃宗澤做嘅大部分角色，最記得係跛co同秋炳（電影等我愛你）<br />\n其實我覺得佢做戲好自然，演乜似乜冇違和又可以忠又可以奸，慘劇笑劇都handle到，但香港人永遠剩係記得佢啲柒嘢笑9佢"},{"pid":"70a324d77f3c4f1b6d1689cc20e1df69f6f2796b","tid":440111,"uid":17484,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"反黑 招積 張建聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f758ed9b037a4b95fff03dec8d96301b51cd685","tid":440111,"uid":110969,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三萬蚊 過夜</span>"},{"pid":"a5fdce3528ed3a72fe6f70dd56f75323abc23947","tid":440111,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"上上下下 左左右右 前前後後 <br />\nOnlyYou<br />\n哦喔哦 俾碌蕉你含 <br />\n你唔夠信念"},{"pid":"f5dab36238ad2cd6e8599df957f898c29e2035ba","tid":440111,"uid":42848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爆裂刑警吳鎮宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果時電視做睇緊爆裂刑警，跟住賣廣告無間道2見倒吳鎮宇，完全係兩個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吳鎮宇呢幾年做戲好似擺脫唔到Sam哥影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我最鐘意佢做難兄難弟扮謝賢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吳鎮宇skinhead頭果期真係最fit,鎗火,爆裂,梁山伯,<br />\n連公元2000呢啲配角都演得好有魅力,搶哂戲<br />\n小本製作逆我者死,收數王又識自己搵戲演,好癲<br />\n近幾年都真係要角色有發揮先睇到吳鎮宇演技功力,<br />\n啲大陸爛片爛角色佢真係同你hea做,<br />\n不過佢近年做返多港產片,使徒行者,衝鋒車都交足貨,<br />\n脫皮爸爸直頭係驚喜,係電影公司笨柒博上屆金像獎,<br />\n今年上嘅話對手又弱,呼聲肯定高幾班(當然金像獎係閪獎就大家都知,純粹係講宣傳策略)"},{"pid":"037a83c886f10f1123c565436c21aef54e9bb011","tid":440111,"uid":130251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"我要揸GTR"},{"pid":"b49194ba0a5218853848923f5406f4dc9bae0679","tid":440111,"uid":39812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T20:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆裂刑警吳鎮宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果時電視做睇緊爆裂刑警，跟住賣廣告無間道2見倒吳鎮宇，完全係兩個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本冇嘢係應該，冇嘢係唔應該<br />\n<br />\n出嚟行，預咗要還<br />\n<br />\n等我，我番黎食飯"},{"pid":"694a92e1c2b7f76a066deb0da7a7a5c9b7be10d0","tid":440111,"uid":36236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T20:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>爆裂刑警吳鎮宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果時電視做睇緊爆裂刑警，跟住賣廣告無間道2見倒吳鎮宇，完全係兩個人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本冇嘢係應該，冇嘢係唔應該<br />\n<br />\n出嚟行，預咗要還<br />\n<br />\n等我，我番黎食飯</blockquote><br />\n入左錢就出一罐汽水，我要既野就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n第一次睇係夜媽媽一個人係屋企睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點解呢套戲好深刻<br />\n<br />\n加上中間賣廣告見倒佢無間道2個feel完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果下覺得佢好神"},{"pid":"cabc34135ee9c3370d1587caf09af549300e33e9","tid":440111,"uid":36236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T20:43:11.000Z","msg":"上面有巴打話脫皮爸爸有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身未聽過呢套戲，留意下先thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074834d3f1b4f97a1f72f724d5c25916c58de3aa","tid":440111,"uid":35693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反黑 招積 張建聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結局出返黎成日形住佢係扮jokor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過張建聲又做向西我已經留意佢<br />\n佢之後拍一獄一世界尊登走去增肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有heart<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb9bf515282166b68f89df1947c8d5c6d21629c","tid":440111,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近年真係鷲哥,overact得嚟好有壓場感,好過癮</blockquote><br />\n入黎就係想講鷲哥 見到真人都係營住佢都係好似高天鷲咁既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死臭雞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"fbef29b15737c05676c7ddc59a5baa6b21a93c35","tid":440111,"uid":35693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T22:29:31.000Z","msg":"仲有趙永洪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一見到佢我就諗起同事三分親做Macro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近拍同囚做勞教好仆街"},{"pid":"8ab67d4f2ab176ff8c7f02d54456c73a2c3a0dab","tid":440111,"uid":35732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:10:20.000Z","msg":"楊怡 宮心計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好睇到一個點"},{"pid":"d2597f1800a0c82533cd081065367aec5045ffdb","tid":440111,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃宗澤做嘅大部分角色，最記得係跛co同秋炳（電影等我愛你）<br />\n其實我覺得佢做戲好自然，演乜似乜冇違和又可以忠又可以奸，慘劇笑劇都handle到，但香港人永遠剩係記得佢啲柒嘢笑9佢</blockquote><br />\n但佢做戲最大問題係唔入戲 比較表面 無個種共鳴<br />\n唔會話佢差 但唔會當佢係好好嘅電視演員"},{"pid":"bf8a067e200336b285ff1d5adda51aad5a24afc2","tid":440111,"uid":45774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:24:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>楊怡 宮心計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好睇到一個點</blockquote><br />\n個眼神凌厲到兩粒眼珠跌出黎<br />\n佢其他戲自然好多"},{"pid":"8d2354b1c8e809db41b636610e0d4fcb5ce81eb5","tid":440111,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>楊怡 宮心計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好睇到一個點</blockquote><br />\n個眼神凌厲到兩粒眼珠跌出黎<br />\n佢其他戲自然好多</blockquote><br />\n大唐雙龍傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278ed3b6af17135465f996c51b48c9d32ad48297","tid":440111,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:31:30.000Z","msg":"佘詩曼係使徒1 老母x3死左喊個幕真係好撚勁<br />\n另外宮心計皇上保佢孩兒個陣 同陳豪對望個眼神又係用對眼做戲<br />\n<br />\n另外鮑姐係天水圍的日與夜個幾場喊戲實而不華 發自內心 好有共嗚"},{"pid":"8e